    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "So I noticed two issues.\r\n\r\nOne is this log `I0407 00:49:44.942492 usb.go:93] handle_events: error: libusb: interrupted [code -10]`. See also: https://github.com/golemfactory/golem/issues/971.\r\n\r\nThe second issue is related to Ledger Nano S. In general if geth is running in the background Ledger is blocked and not usable by other applications (MyEtherWallet, Ledger Wallet). This happens also in Ledger is no in the mode compatible with geth (no Ethereum app running, or Ethereum application in \"browser\" mode).\r\n\r\nI can do more testing if needed.",
